inties. This result\ndemonstrates that the LAE statistics of GRB hosts may give us useful\ninformation in the future.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 May 2009 02:16:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 4 Nov 2009 07:30:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-12-15"}
