y reflect intrinsic differences, but could be strongly influenced\nby the increasing effect of inverse-Compton cooling of extended radio jets at\nhigh redshift.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 May 2009 12:00:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-13"}
